item.description:
You all are invited to the 3rd Annual Seacoast Area End of Summer Liberty Bash: Sunday September 6, 1:00 PM to ???.

This kid-friendly, pet-friendly, liberty-friendly party will be hosted at the home of Honey & Todd Puterbaugh at 68 Beauty Hill Road, Barrington, NH. Look for the Gadsden flag.

Please bring a dish to share and your beverage of choice. Grills will be available for cooking. If possible, please bring a folding chair, too. Games and musical instruments are encouraged.

Please spread the word to any liberty-lovin' friends.

Thanks. Hope to see you there.

-Todd
item.name: 3rd Annual Seacoast Area End of Summer Liberty Bash
